productText.text:
An easy way get your veggies every day! 2 full servings of vegetables in every 11.5 oz. can*
 

*11.5 fl. oz. juice provides more than 2 servings (1/2 cup each) of vegetables. The 2010 Dietary Guidelines for Americans recommend 2 1/2 cups of a variety of vegetables per day for a 2,000 calorie diet.
